  "title": "Legal Secretary",
  "description": "<p>1. Providing administrative support to one or more lawyers.</p>\n<p>2. Assisting with court filings and facilitating the meeting of deadlines by monitoring, maintaining, and updating calendar and providing timely reminders for lawyers.</p>\n<p>3. File and organize legal documents in a timely manner.</p>\n<p>4. Answering calls, taking messages and handling correspondence. Also, assist with arranging meetings and conference calls.</p>\n<p>5. Preparation of invoices and expense reimbursements.</p>\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n<p>1. Have good communication, administrative and organisational skills.</p>\n<p>2. Familiarity with legal documents and terminology would be preferred.</p>\n<p>3. Good command of spoken and written English.</p>\n<p>4. Proficiency with Microsoft Office programs.</p>\n<p>5. Able to effectively prioritize and meet deadlines.</p>",
